name: 安杰拉·恩茨明格
name_full: 安杰拉·恩茨明格 Angela Entzminger

last_movies.title: 我与超人的冒险 第一季

introduction: Angela Entzminger is a Los Angeles-based television writer and storyboard artist. Her writing credits include work for Warner Bros. Animation's upcoming HBO Max series "My Adventures with Superman" and for Nickelodeon Animation Studios' hit bridge series Santiago of the Seas. Her storyboard credits include work for Nickelodeon Animation Studios popular series The Loud House, Santiago of the Seas and for Titmouse's upcoming sci-fi adult comedy The Hospital.
